Meet <b>Joey Jan</b>, our Citizen of the Week!<br><br>She's a friendly girl who has lived in Lakeview since July 26, 2006. Her home at <a href='/home/?user=joeyjan1444'>8904-A Bluebird Street</a> is colorfully decorated and has plenty of room for her to pursue her favorite hobbies. She is a great student, a generous friend, and definitely someone everyone should meet!<br><br>Joey Jan loves the colors green, red, and yellow, and her beautiful, comfortable home is full of them! Her yellow sofa is her favorite place to curl up with a good book, and her friends love to hang out in the green guest room. She's an avid reader who is also great at crossword puzzles &mdash; a skill some of her friends envy her for.<br><br>When she's not hanging out at home listening to pop, soft rock, or disco, she likes to get together with friends for pizza parties. Plain cheese pizza is her favorite, but she doesn't have it all the time because she likes to keep her diet balanced. And she has learned that by letting herself eat it only once in a while, she enjoys it that much more!<br><br>Joey Jan's regular exercise schedule keeps her in great shape. Try rope-racing against her and she'll surprise you with her speed! With a natural competitive streak, she is a force to be reckoned with, and energizes those around her.<br><br>Thanks for being a great citizen, Joey Jan, and congratulations on being named Citizen of the Week!<br></div>
